-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7130b485-0919-414c-b06b-0139ae43ce9c_3264x1836.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:722,&quot;bytes&quot;:2451261,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7130b485-0919-414c-b06b-0139ae43ce9c_3264x1836.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7130b485-0919-414c-b06b-0139ae43ce9c_3264x1836.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7130b485-0919-414c-b06b-0139ae43ce9c_3264x1836.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7130b485-0919-414c-b06b-0139ae43ce9c_3264x1836.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=User:Lightak&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1">Lightak</a>的“ <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=52016172">Alderson Broaddus</a> ”， <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/?ref=openverse">CC BY-SA 4.0</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这些天我的每周综述来得有点晚了，因为我正在处理另一个兔子的健康问题；我剩下的兔子吉格斯背部有椎间盘突出。这是收养在恶劣条件下长大的救援兔的不幸缺点，尤其是当它们开始变老时。不管怎样，我们正在努力让他早日康复。</p><p>一如既往，我们以播客开始本周的综述。<a href="https://link.chtbl.com/Econ102">本周由 Erik Torenberg 主持的 Econ 102 节目</a>主要讲述中国经济放缓。这是 Spotify 链接： </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8afc652b3f806b5aa076b8f34c&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;E8: Why China is Primed for Economic Carnage Worse than the US Financial Crisis of 2008&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/6hSV68nYSwaD9KjEKyVvZZ&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/6hSV68nYSwaD9KjEKyVvZZ" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>这里是<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/e8-why-china-is-primed-for-economic-carnage-worse-than/id1696419056?i=1000626051918">苹果</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1dwvbMStp-g">YouTube</a> 。</p><p>无论如何，继续本周的综述。我至少暂时将这些切换为非付费墙。</p><h4> 1. 大学洗牌及其背后的市场力量</h4><p>多年来，我一直宣扬大学扩张可以解决困扰美国的许多问题——地区经济差距、创新低下，甚至社会问题。但在过去的几年里，我开始意识到<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/americans-are-falling-out-of-love">这是行不通的</a>。原因是需求萎缩；美国的年轻人数量已趋于稳定，大学入学率正在下降。需求萎缩导致价格下降（<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/five-big-trends-that-have-changed">实际学费下降</a>），并导致大学关闭。 <a href="https://www.cleveland.com/news/2023/08/west-virginia-college-announces-plan-to-close-weeks-before-new-school-year.html">最近的例子</a>是西弗吉尼亚州的奥尔德森布罗德斯大学，该大学由于严重的财务困难而即将关闭。排名较低的州立学校也开始遭受洗牌——西弗吉尼亚大学正在<a href="https://www.thenation.com/article/society/wvu-cuts-higher-education/">削减师资和项目</a>。</p><p>一些政治呼喊者肯定会抓住这一趋势，作为他们对“觉醒”美国大学的负面看法的理由。但我认为最大的因素可能只是大学不再像以前那样是一笔划算的经济交易。似乎是为了强调这一点，旧金山联邦储备银行进行了<a href="https://www.frbsf.org/economic-research/publications/economic-letter/2023/august/falling-college-wage-premiums-by-race-and-ethnicity/">一项新的分析</a>，记录了大学工资溢价的下降。保费在 2010 年代趋于稳定，目前正在下降。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg" width="550" height="365" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:365,&quot;width&quot;:550,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:23196,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F998d34d2-02e3-4914-baa1-43665f5d0f4c_550x365.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.frbsf.org/economic-research/publications/economic-letter/2023/august/falling-college-wage-premiums-by-race-and-ethnicity/">顺丰联储</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这种下降发生在各个种族群体中。</p><p>不过，在我们得出这是坏消息的结论之前，我们应该意识到，下降的一个重要原因是，过去十年中，工薪阶层的收入增长速度快于受过大学教育的人的收入增长速度： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg" width="550" height="365" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:365,&quot;width&quot;:550,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:35474,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa00bc0f0-d9c6-4cdb-b647-7dc894a8ca02_550x365.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.frbsf.org/economic-research/publications/economic-letter/2023/august/falling-college-wage-premiums-by-race-and-ethnicity/">顺丰联储</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>现在下结论还为时过早，但 2008 年的金融危机和随后的经济衰退可能标志着长达 30 年的人力资本时代的结束，在这个时代，知识产业主导着其他一切，你需要学位才能蓬勃发展。如果是这样，这对美国的经济平等来说是个好消息，但对大学来说却是个坏消息，因为大学从在知识产业经济中发挥的关键作用中获益匪浅。</p><p>当然，这只是一个坏消息——总体而言，大学仍将是我们国家的关键机构之一，对好学校名额的需求仍然很高。但我现在悲观地认为，大学部门的大规模扩张是拯救该国衰落地区的良药。</p><h4> 2.中国在发展中国家中交的朋友不多</h4><p>金砖国家峰会让一些人相信，中国正在发起一场成功的魅力攻势；尽管<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/brics-is-fake">金砖国家从根本上来说是假的</a>，但一些国家想加入这个假俱乐部这一事实可能表明它们将中国视为仁慈的霸主。中国外交部一直在<a href="https://twitter.com/MFA_China/status/1695061348827152806">努力宣扬</a>中国是世界发展中国家的领导者这一理念。</p><p>但与此同时，中国一直在采取激怒和疏远其地区发展中国家的行动。例如，它<a href="https://twitter.com/globaltimesnews/status/1696104724691570945">最近发布了</a>中国的“标准地图”，其中包括印度、不丹、越南、印度尼西亚、马来西亚和菲律宾的部分（以及俄罗斯、日本、文莱，当然还有整个台湾的部分）。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg" width="690" height="813" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:813,&quot;width&quot;:690,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:162308,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F62edd201-d062-4d3b-8b3a-a2feab38f111_690x813.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>事实证明——惊喜！ ——大多数国家不喜欢你声称他们的领土是你自己的。因此，越南<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/08/31/india/india-china-map-protest-intl-hnk/index.html">、印度、马来西亚、菲律宾</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/CollinSLKoh/status/1697165608184684780">印度尼西亚</a>都对<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-08-31/vietnam-opposes-new-china-map-claiming-south-china-sea-islands">中国的地图提出了抗议</a>。正如<a href="https://twitter.com/tanvi_madan/status/1697250829596770579">坦维·马丹</a>和许多其他人所指出的那样，领土扩张主义并不完全是赢得朋友和影响人们的方式。</p><p>中国越来越多地表明，这些扩张主义的领土主张不仅仅是纸上谈兵，而是它打算积极追求的主张。中国海警正在对中国声称拥有主权的越南岛屿附近的<a href="https://twitter.com/GordianKnotRay/status/1696908463354593615">越南渔船进行水炮轰击</a>，并将<a href="https://twitter.com/GordianKnotRay/status/1696237091435462674">船只</a>派往越南海域。这正是中国对菲律宾使用的“切香肠”策略，只不过菲律宾有盟友美国<a href="https://www.state.gov/u-s-support-for-the-philippines-in-the-south-china-sea-5/">做后盾</a>。越南是一个独立国家，这可能就是为什么它热衷于在拜登下个月访问该国时与美国签署<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/08/28/politics/joe-biden-vietnam-visit/index.html">战略伙伴关系协议</a>的原因。</p><p>无论如何，很明显，中国的扩张主义立场优先于任何将自己描绘成发展中国家领导人的外交举措。也许拉丁美洲或中东的一些国家——远离中国军舰，并且仍然对美国在那里的干涉主义遗产感到痛苦——会买账。但在亚洲这个世界关键战略地区，他们不会这样做。</p><h4> 3、“僵尸”企业会拖累中国经济吗？</h4><p>当中国经济增长依然强劲时，批评中国经济模式的文章没有那么多读者；既然它正在遭受可能是长期的放缓，每个人都急于解释问题出在哪里。 <a href="https://braddelong.substack.com/p/draft-what-is-going-on-wi-chinas">Brad DeLong</a>和<a href="https://danieldrezner.substack.com/p/the-end-of-the-rise-of-china">Dan Drezner</a>对许多正在撰写的文章进行了很好的综述。所有这些都很好，值得一读。</p><p>但<a href="https://arpitrage.substack.com/p/whats-going-on-with-chinas-stagnation">Arpit Gupta 的帖子</a>可能是最独特的，因为它提出了一些我以前从未见过很多人谈论过的问题（在 Arpit 抢先一步之前我就打算写下来！）。</p><p> （首先，做一个简短的更正。阿尔皮特让我联想到对中国经济放缓的两种观点：“专制征用风险”观点和“房地产繁荣-萧条”观点。第二种是正确的；<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-chinas-economy-ran-off-the-rails">我确实认为房地产是主要的经济增长点。但是</a>，尽管<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-is-china-smashing-its-tech-industry">我在 2021 年写了一篇关于中国科技打击的热门文章</a>，但我不认为这是造成中国经济放缓的主要原因；这实际上只是说明了习近平的想法以及原因<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/what-if-xi-jinping-just-isnt-that">他不太能干</a>。）</p><p>不管怎样，阿尔皮特对中国经济放缓有自己的解释，这就是他所说的“软预算约束”。这是大多数经济学家所说的“僵尸公司”的一个礼貌用语，即如果失败的公司继续维持生命，它们最终会降低生产率。他们通过扭曲激励（如果你知道你不会失败，你就不会建立一个高效的企业）和掠夺生产力更高的公司的资源和市场份额来做到这一点。阿尔皮特认为这就是中国正在发生的事情：</p><blockquote><p>最终你会陷入长期的“短缺”状况，因为所有公司都得到了救助，并在财务可行性很久之后继续作为僵尸实体运营（并需要更多投入）。共产党永远不能承诺在这里进行硬市场改革，这将不可避免地导致政治统治的结束。</p><p>好吧，中国有什么证据可以证明这一点？ </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png" width="943" height="649" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:649,&quot;width&quot;:943,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4f862597-3ae0-41f1-a19b-9a724cd07250_943x649.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>纵观整个制造企业，全球金融危机后的窗口期，全要素生产率大幅下降，有两个因素驱动。首先，<em>新</em>企业的全要素生产率增长大幅下降，表明企业进入不再那么依赖于纯粹的经济因素。其次，我们看到退出维度的全要素生产率增长为负——通过淘汰非生产性企业来提高生产率在中国并没有发生。</p></blockquote><p>阿尔皮特将僵尸化视为共产主义经济的一个特征，虽然共产主义可能会让情况变得更糟，但僵尸化是一个众所周知的故事，也困扰着其他国家。 Caballero、Hoshi 和 Kashyap 在<a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w12129">2006 年发表了一篇精彩的论文，</a>解释了日本的银行如何受到激励，向 20 世纪 90 年代亏损的公司提供“常青”贷款，导致“僵尸企业”过度增长，侵占了劳动力、资本和市场份额，并从根本上阻碍了日本企业家的发展。培养一批新的更高效的冠军。尽管日本银行大多不再这样做，但日本政府在 2010 年代介入，提供了<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2016-01-20/japan-must-let-zombie-companies-die?sref=R8NfLgwS">大量救助资金</a>，将效率低下的公司从破产中拯救出来，仅仅是为了保持高就业水平。</p><p>就造成中国当前经济放缓的原因而言，我仍然将最大的责任归咎于房地产。 Arpit 在<a href="https://documents1.worldbank.org/curated/en/839401593007627879/pdf/Chinas-Productivity-Slowdown-and-Future-Growth-Potential.pdf">2020 年世界银行报告</a>中获得的生产率图表显示，整个商业部门只对增量资本产出率的增长（即保持增长所需的投资额增加）做出了一小部分贡献。最近几年。大部分原因是住房和基础设施效率降低，尽管它们从商业部门占用了更多资本： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg" width="1132" height="661" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:661,&quot;width&quot;:1132,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:166209,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F47edbcb4-e3f9-416b-a718-9dc4817bdeef_1132x661.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://documents1.worldbank.org/curated/en/839401593007627879/pdf/Chinas-Productivity-Slowdown-and-Future-Growth-Potential.pdf">世界银行</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><em>（向世界银行快速说明：什么样的疯子会在具有相同部门细分的两个相邻图表上重新排列配色方案？图表犯罪！）</em></p><p>但我确实相信，僵尸化<a href="https://www.piie.com/blogs/china-economic-watch/china-only-nibbling-problem-zombie-state-owned-enterprises">一直</a>是中国<a href="https://econ.columbia.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/41/2018/10/Job-Market-Paper-Qiuying-Qu-190110.pdf">悄然</a>形成的<a href="https://www.imf.org/-/media/Files/Publications/WP/2017/wp17266.ashx">趋势</a>，而且未来可能会成为一个更大的问题。伴随着老龄化、城市化进程的终结以及国际社会对中国工业的强烈抵制，这将成为阻碍中国在房地产问题解决很久之后恢复发展中国家增长率的阻力之一。</p><h4> 4. YIMBY 思想之战的胜利</h4><p>过去几年，该国最令人鼓舞的草根政治运动是 YIMBY 运动，该运动专注于具体目标（建造更多住房），而不是政治意识形态。近年来，他们<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-long-march-of-the-yimbys">赢得了多项立法胜利</a>，而且这一趋势<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-21a">似乎正在加速</a>。我计划继续报道这一趋势</p><p>在我看来，与立法之战同样重要的是<em>公共关系之</em>战，YIMBY 也赢得了这场战争。单户住宅分区对住房建设的有害影响已经从一种边缘观念变成了<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/08/05/business/single-family-zoning-laws">传统观念</a>。尽管“左翼人士”在这款以前被称为 Twitter 的应用程序上发出了尖锐的尖叫声，他们认为增加住房供应代表了一种“涓滴经济学”，但拜登政府现在<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/07/27/politics/biden-administration-housing-moves/index.html">坚定地同意</a>增加供应的必要性。</p><p>与此同时，随着大量新研究的不断涌入，YIMBY 也赢得了这场<em>智力</em>战，这些研究支持了建造更多住房可以带来广泛共享繁荣的观点。例如，<a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0094119023000244">一项关于新西兰奥克兰全市升级分区的研究</a>发现，升级分区大大增加了建筑面积。我们还不知道对租金的影响，但这令人鼓舞，因为它表明仅仅通过允许建造就可以获得更多的住房供应。与此同时， <a href="https://www.urbanlab.ibf.uu.se/research-projects/new-housing-construction-and-the-concentration-of-affluence/">Liang 和 Kindström 的一项研究</a>发现，新住房建设<a href="https://www.urbanlab.ibf.uu.se/urban-facts/">有利于所有收入群体的人们</a>：</p><blockquote><p>新建住房通常价格昂贵，而且主要是高收入人群搬进其中……新建住房能否创建移动链，为低收入人群腾出住房？……我们的研究结果表明，新建住房的好处平均分配在不同收入群体的居民之间。尽管获得新住房的主要是高收入人群，但这些住房会产生连锁反应，间接改善低收入人群的住房选择。梁哲源表示，其中一种解释是，收入较低的人比收入较高的人搬家更频繁，这意味着他们更经常参与搬家链并利用新住房带来的空置。</p></blockquote><p>这正是YIMBYs所说的“过滤”和反YIMBYs诽谤为“涓滴”的效果，我称之为<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/yuppie-fishtanks-yimbyism-explained">“雅皮鱼缸”效应</a>。</p><p>至此，我们也有机会观察了少数几个实际上齐心协力允许更多住房的美国城市。其中包括弗吉尼亚州阿灵顿、西雅图和明尼阿波利斯。当然，他们的尝试比奥克兰或<a href="https://jamesjgleeson.wordpress.com/2018/02/19/how-tokyo-built-its-way-to-abundant-housing/">东京</a>的尝试要温和得多，但仍然令人鼓舞。</p><p>艾米丽·汉密尔顿（Emily Hamilton）<a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/how-dc-densified">在《作品进行中》（Works in Progress）上发表了一篇精彩的文章</a>，其中她解释了阿灵顿住宅建设工作的政策和政治。我强烈建议阅读整篇文章。一个有趣的趣闻是，阿灵顿基本上与富有的邻避者达成了一项协议，允许他们保留低密度的小岛屿，以换取他们支持整个城市的升级分区。这种肮脏、不公平的“香肠是如何制作的”细节在许多讨论中都被忽视了，但考虑到邻避势力在美国的根深蒂固和强大，一些城市可能会发现这些细节很有用。无论如何，汉密尔顿表明，与其他大型“超级明星城市”相比，华盛顿都会区（包括阿灵顿）和西雅图建造了更多的多户住宅，并且经历了更高的“供应弹性”——价格仍然上涨，因为很多人搬进来，但相对于人口增长，物价涨幅较小。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg" width="919" height="485" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/fd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:485,&quot;width&quot;:919,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:113289,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd6bee69-62fa-47b3-a7ec-03b80210db7c_919x485.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/how-dc-densified">艾米丽·汉密尔顿</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>我强烈推荐的另一篇优秀文章是<a href="https://onefinaleffort.com/blog/a-detailed-look-at-minneapolis-housing-supply-reforms">马修·马尔特曼对明尼阿波利斯住房改革的分析</a>。他认为，虽然大肆宣扬的废除单户住宅区划的影响不大，但它是对供应产生重大影响的一揽子改革计划之一。他指出，自这些改革生效以来，明尼阿波利斯的租金相对于附近城市有所下降： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa56fb715-4082-4355-90c0-b0b991e394c0_847x499.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpubl