><p>但作为一名美国乐观主义者，如果我不指出那些<em>不</em>顺利的事情，就会给我的国家带来伤害。我们需要庆祝我们的成功和优势，但我们也需要弥补我们的弱点。美国最大的弱点之一是预期寿命。与其他富裕国家相比，美国人的寿命要年轻得多。我们的预期寿命多年来一直落后，但自大流行开始以来，这一差距几乎增加了一倍： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f264a8c-95d1-407e-bf6e-a9935d63c0da_900x864.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f264a8c-95d1-407e-bf6e-a9935d63c0da_900x864.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f264a8c-95d1-407e-bf6e-a9935d63c0da_900x864.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f264a8c-95d1-407e-bf6e-a9935d63c0da_900x864.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f264a8c-95d1-407e-bf6e-a9935d63c0da_900x864.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f264a8c-95d1-407e-bf6e-a9935d63c0da_900x864.jpeg" width="676" height="648.96" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7f264a8c-95d1-407e-bf6e-a9935d63c0da_900x864.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:864,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot