media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7510dfb0-8d59-4059-91c1-33351c29def3_1011x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7510dfb0-8d59-4059-91c1-33351c29def3_1011x795.jpeg" width="1011" height="795" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7510dfb0-8d59-4059-91c1-33351c29def3_1011x795.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:795,&quot;width&quot;:1011,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:101604,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7510dfb0-8d59-4059-91c1-33351c29def3_1011x795.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7510dfb0-8d59-4059-91c1-33351c29def3_1011x795.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7510dfb0-8d59-4059-91c1-33351c29def3_1011x795.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7510dfb0-8d59-4059-91c1-33351c29def3_1011x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/BX.KLT.DINV.WD.GD.ZS?end=2022&amp;locations=CN&amp;start=1990">世界银行</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>20世纪90年代和2000年代的出口和外国直接投资增长战略的收益递减可能会大幅减缓中国的增长。因此，中国领导人做出了转变，用房地产投资取代了部分工厂投资。政府告诉银行要大量放贷，以避免经济衰退，而他们知道如何向其注入资金的大多数公司都以某种方式从事房地产业务。这一策略成功地避免了 2008-10 年的经济衰退，并且在接下来的十年中，每当危险似乎威胁时，中国都会再次使用该策略——例如 2015 年股市崩盘后。</p><p>也许中国领导人担心如果增长放缓会给他们带来什么后果，或者也许他们并没有真正考虑过这项政策的代价可能有多大。无论如何，<strong>中国基本上从出口导向型经济<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/real-estate-is-chinas-economic-achilles">转向房地产导向型经济</a></strong>。房地产相关产业占总产值的比重飙升至近30%。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg" width="775" height="652" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:652,&quot;width&quot;:775,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:102327,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3e96694b-0d2e-48cc-a554-7787cd28bc7e_775x652.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://scholar.harvard.edu/sites/scholar.harvard.edu/files/rogoff/files/nber_27697_peak_china_housing_1.pdf">Rogoff &amp; Yang (2020)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这一转向使中国免于2010年代的衰退，但也带来了一些意想不到的负面后果。首先，建筑及相关行业的生产率增长往往低于其他行业（原因尚不100%明确）。因此，继续将国家的劳动力和资本资源转移到这些行业最终会降低总生产率的增长。全要素生产率在 2000 年代稳步增长，但在 2010 年代突然持平： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png" width="1318" height="450" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:450,&quot;width&quot;:1318,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:41365,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F40904470-6695-4fd0-adb6-530b29846b3b_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这些 TFP 数据有点可疑，但更乐观的消息来源也<a href="https://www.lowyinstitute.org/publications/revising-down-rise-china">记录了 2010 年代生产率急剧下降</a>。</p><p>这种生产力下降可能<em>不仅仅是</em>由于房地产——随着中国侵占了所有更容易的东西，复制外国技术开始变得更加困难。生产力并不是影响中国经济增长的唯一因素——大约在同一时间，农村剩余劳动力枯竭。不管怎样，把所有这些放在一起，你会发现 2010 年代 GDP 增长放缓，从 10% 左右降至 6% 或 7% 左右： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg" width="1020" height="844" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:844,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:97190,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b0d7ba8-b1b2-493f-b013-1583974664af_1020x844.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.KD.ZG?end=2019&amp;locations=CN&amp;start=1991">世界银行</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>但 6-7% 仍然相当快。为了保持这样的增长速度，中国必须进行<em>大量</em>投资——<a href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NE.GDI.TOTL.ZS?locations=CN">约占其GDP的43%</a> ，比2000年代初期的辉煌时期<a href="https://www.ft.com/content/e46a6f4a-2073-343b-ac82-2e3084a4b9eb">还要多，也比日本和韩国在各自工业发展的相似阶段要多得多。</a> 。</p><p>只是中国并没有有效地配置这些资本，而是将其投入到回报率越来越低的房地产领域。私营企业的资产回报率暴跌： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg" width="951" height="460" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:460,&quot;width&quot;:951,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:65091,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F57684b42-c64e-45c5-b110-75d3d89b99af_951x460.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.bruegel.org/policy-brief/can-chinese-growth-defy-gravity">勃鲁盖尔</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这种下降很大程度上是由于中国经济转向房地产。如果剔除房地产，私营部门的恶化看起来<a href="https://documents1.worldbank.org/curated/en/839401593007627879/pdf/Chinas-Productivity-Slowdown-and-Future-Growth-Potential.pdf">就不那么严重了</a>。</p><p>许多评论员会谈论中国需要承担越来越多的债务才能保持一定的增长。我更喜欢从投资的角度来思考。由于其重心从出口转向房地产，中国必须继续在实体建筑（公寓楼、办公室、商店和基础设施）上投资越来越多的资本，才能将增长保持在 6-7% 的范围内。</p><p>或者正如<a href="https://documents1.worldbank.org/curated/en/839401593007627879/pdf/Chinas-Productivity-Slowdown-and-Future-Growth-Potential.pdf">世界银行在 2020 年所说的</a>那样：</p><blockquote><p> [产生一定增长量所需的新资本]的增加很大程度上可以用基础设施和房地产资本回报率较低来解释。在[增量资本产出比]迅速恶化的这些年里，中国的投资构成发生了显着变化。商业部门的资本形成份额下降，而基础设施和住房领域的份额上升。</p></blockquote><p>无论如何，中国转向房地产的同时减缓了生产率的增长，同时也引发了巨大的泡沫。由于房地产也是中国人的主要储蓄工具，人们将毕生的积蓄——以及他们父母毕生的积蓄、祖父母毕生的积蓄——投入到购买公寓中，他们希望这些公寓不仅可以作为居住的地方，而且可以作为他们的生活。退休储蓄（或者可能从影子银行购买房地产支持的债券）。</p><p>就像2008年之前的美国一样，长期的繁荣可能会欺骗2010年代的中国人，让他们认为房地产价格会一直上涨——这种现象被称为<a href="https://scholar.harvard.edu/files/shleifer/files/extrapolation_bubbles_published_version.pdf">外推预期</a>。结果，人们在中国的大城市购买公寓的价格是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/real-estate-is-chinas-economic-achilles">其年收入的 18 至 50 倍</a>，远远高于旧金山或纽约。</p><p>所以基本上存在一个巨大的泡沫，最终泡沫必须破裂。目前尚不清楚究竟是什么导致了这一现象——一些人指责习近平在 2021 年对工业进行了笨手笨脚的镇压，而<a href="https://scholar.harvard.edu/sites/scholar.harvard.edu/files/rogoff/files/nber_27697_peak_china_housing_1.pdf">另一些人则表示，这是中国人均居住空间达到发达国家水平的自然结果</a>。我们可能永远不会知道。但它确实流行起来，现在价格正在下降，债务没有得到偿还，开发商违约，影子银行违约，贷款直线下降，等等——所有这些都是美国在 2008-10 年和日本看到的情况90年代初经历过。在这一点上，房地产泡沫及其后果是一个非常明显的现象。</p><p>因此，尽管转向房地产导致中国经济增长长期放缓，但它也产生了泡沫，最终导致短期急剧放缓。如果说中国的经济困境有一个大统一的理论的话，那就是“房地产太多”。</p><p>但为什么？中国的政治经济又是如何让他们走上这条路的呢？正如美国和日本所了解到的那样，房地产泡沫是许多经济体都会发生的事情，但中国的房地产行业看起来要膨胀得多。我认为中国允许这种情况发生至少有两个基本原因。</p><p>首先，拒绝刺激房地产以应对出口导向型增长的结束、2008 年金融危机以及后来的经济威胁，可能会带来经济衰退的风险。在民主国家，经济衰退通常会导致执政党下台。在独裁国家，他们可能会被扔出窗外。因此，中国的威权体制可能迫使他们采取短视的行动，容忍零衰退风险，尽管这样做会带来长期成本。</p><p>中国转向房地产的第二个原因是，这有助于地方政府支付费用。中国没有房产税，因此地方政府需要出售土地来支付服务费用。向开发商提供大量银行贷款无疑增加了对土地的需求，使地方政府能够获得更多收入。</p><p>不管怎样，我用这个简单的故事来解释为什么中国经济在发展初期就放缓了，然后在 2020 年代初经历了崩溃。出口拉动和外国直接投资拉动的增长不可能永远持续下去，当它们耗尽时，最好将资本转移到建立高科技制造业和服务业的均衡经济上，而不是将其投入房地产开发商和影子银行。转向房地产最终将损害经济。尽管谈论中国的“百年计划”之类的东西，他们还是掉进了脚下的坑里。</p><p>真实的故事会比这更复杂，但如果你想快速而简单地解释为什么现在每个人都在关注中国的经济崩溃，我认为转向房地产的故事可能是最好的简单故事你可以知道。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-chinas-economy-ran-off-the-rails?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-chinas-economy-ran-off-the-rails?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>; 
