//substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f533a66-9070-46a9-88b4-f07d199d1a6d_655x664.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f533a66-9070-46a9-88b4-f07d199d1a6d_655x664.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：Mabli 等人。 (2013) 通过<a href="https://www.cbpp.org/research/food-assistance/snap-is-linked-with-improved-nutritional-outcomes-and-lower-health-care">CBPP</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>所以，一方面，这……并不令人惊奇？您可能会认为，只要为人们提供所需的所有食物，就能将粮食不安全状况减少五分之一以上。这种微小的影响说明了美国贫困问题的复杂性，以及通过简单干预措施解决贫困问题的难度。</p><p>但即使食品券<em>不能解决</em>饥饿问题，它们也肯定会减少饥饿。到 2022 年，成本将达到 1194 亿美元，这一成本并不巨大。如果您担心人们在街上挨饿，那么您绝对应该保留这个计划，即使我们确实需要对其进行调整以鼓励更健康的饮食。</p><h4>自杀和取消文化</h4><p>这就留下了安东尼抱怨的另外两个社会问题：自杀和取消文化。</p><p>其中第一个问题无疑是一个主要问题。安东尼唱道“年轻人把自己埋在六英尺深的地下/因为这个该死的国家所做的就是不断把他们踢倒”。我不知道他的理由是否正确，但事实证明他是对的。自杀率创<a href="https://people.com/suicides-in-the-us-reached-new-high-2022-cdc-report-7642827">历史新高</a>，男性自杀率远高于女性，而且差距还在扩大： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg" width="560" height="306" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:306,&quot;width&quot;:560,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:25385,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w